---

<section class="stats-band-section">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">The engineer behind the work</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">From solo tools to production systems.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-number">6+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Years building</span>
        <p class="stat-desc">From first commit to production systems serving real users.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-number">30</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Open-source repos</span>
        <p class="stat-desc">Tools, APIs, and deep-dives, shipped in the open for anyone to use.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-number">290+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">GitHub stars</span>
        <p class="stat-desc">Quiet proof the next person hit the same wall, and got a head start.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stats-band-section {
    background: var(--color-surface-dark);
  }

  .inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-section, 96px) var(--space-xl, 32px);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xxl, 48px);
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.88px;
    color: var(--color-on-dark-soft);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm, 12px);
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-on-dark);
    letter-spacing: -1.08px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-base, 16px);
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 12px);
    padding: var(--space-xl, 32px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-on-dark);
    letter-spacing: -1.92px;
    line-height: 1.0;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-on-dark);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs, 8px);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-on-dark-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: var(--space-xs, 8px) 0 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .inner {
      padding: 64px var(--space-base, 16px);
    }

    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
